stitute.  She travels extensively for pleasure and self-education.  At home she is an avid sportswoman, enjoying working with her horses as well as skiing, mountain biking and spending time outdoors.</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.9.5\" _module_preset=\"default\" locked=\"off\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\" _builder_version=\"4.9.5\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.9.5\" _module_preset=\"default\" text_text_color=\"#1d2639\" text_font_size=\"18px\" header_text_color=\"#1d2639\" header_font_size=\"32px\" header_3_font=\"|700|||||||\" header_3_text_color=\"#1d2639\" header_3_font_size=\"24px\"]<h3>Education</h3>\n<p>Ms. Koloušková received her J.D. cum laude from Seattle University School of Law in 1997.  While pursuing her legal education, Ms. Koloušková was a moot court participant and a coach for the school’s regional moot court team. She interned for the Central Puget Sound Growth Management Hearings Board, where she assisted in writing the Board’s first Digest of Decisions.</p>\n<p>Ms. Koloušková graduated from Western Washington University in 1994 where she earned a Bachelor of Arts in History, with an emphasis in African and Classical Studies.</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" _builder_version=\"4.9.5\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.9.5\" _module_preset=\"default\" locked=\"off\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\" _builder_version=\"4.9.5\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.9.5\" _module_preset=\"default\" link_font=\"||||on|||#1d2639|\" link_text_color=\"#1d2639\" link_font_size=\"24px\"]<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.jmmklanduselaw.com/our-people\">Back to All Profiles</a></p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" _builder_version=\"4.9.5\" _module_preset=\"default\" custom_css_main_element=\"font-family: franklin-gothic-urw, sans-serif;\" locked=\"off\"][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.9.5\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\" _builder_version=\"4.9.5\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.9.5\" _module_preset=\"default\" header_font=\"|700|||||||\" header_text_color=\"#272f3f\" header_font_size=\"40px\"]<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Interested in partnering with us?</h1>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_button button_url=\"http://www.jmmklanduselaw.com/contact\" button_text=\"CONTACT US\" button_alignment=\"center\" _builder_version=\"4.9.5\" _module_preset=\"default\" custom_button=\"on\" button_text_color=\"#FFFFFF\" button_bg_color=\"#272f3f\" locked=\"off\"][/et_pb_button][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]','Duana Kolouskova','','inherit','closed','closed','','165-revision-v1','','','2021-06-11 03:11:52','2021-06-11 03:11:52','',165,'http://jmmk-law.local/?p=281',0,'revision','',0);
